data.description: Welcome home to this immaculate & very versatile Sydney floor plan located on a private lot in popular Encore at Eastmark 55+ community! Features 2 master suites, den, plus an optional space for your choice of living/dining or hobby/game room. Extended kitchen boasts gorgeous 42'' white Shaker style cabinets, granite counters, modern glass backsplash, under cabinet lighting, wall oven/micro (New May 2023), gas cooktop, stainless steel refrigerator(stays), large pot drawers, whole home water filtration plus reverse osmosis at the kitchen sink & walk-in pantry. Expansive 12x24'' tile flooring throughout w/upgraded carpet in bedrooms only. Additional upgrades: Energy efficient Solar (Owned), Upgraded HVAC w/whole home air purifier at the unit, surround sound speakers in the family room plus tons of extra cabinets in garage, shutters throughout, framed mirrors in all baths, frameless glass in master shower, double sinks plus huge walk-in closet. Private backyard has extended patio with pavers, artificial turf and is very low maintenance. Enjoy all the amenities the clubhouse has to offer. Within just a 5 minute walk, you will find pickle-ball/tennis courts, state of the art gym, pool/spa, yoga room, craft room and tons of activities to keep you busy everyday! See the Builder/Owner Updates sheet for all the remaining details.
